ast.com, I&#8217;ve met with quite some hurdles and roadblocks. That&#8217;s why I thought it would be a good idea to write a post; so you won&#8217;t have to invent the wheel twice. Define your Intensive Care Pages Although it&#8217;s very tempting to start off your&#8230;</p><p>This post first appeared on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://yoast.com">Yoast</a>. Whoopity Doo!</p>";s:12:"atom_content";s:1:"A";}i:19;a:14:{s:5:"title";s:46:"Content Analysis with the WordPress SEO plugin";s:4:"link";s:122:"http://yoast.com/wordpress-seo-content-analysis/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=wordpress-seo-content-analysis";s:8:"comments";s:57:"http://yoast.com/wordpress-seo-content-analysis/#comments";s:7:"pubdate";s:31:"Thu, 22 Aug 2013 20:20:11 +0000";s:2:"dc";a:1:{s:7:"creator";s:13:"Joost de Valk";}s:8:"category";s:42:"SEOWordPressWordPress PluginsWordPress SEO";s:4:"guid";s:26:"http://yoast.com/?p=101721";s:11:"description";s:432:"<p>We&#8217;ve been rather busy with the WordPress SEO plugin the last few days. We did a release yesterday and a quick follow up today to fix a few collisions with other plugins. Loads of cool small fixes in there, but one in particular that I think is worth highlighting as it&#8217;s something other plugin developers&#8230;</p><p>This post first appeared on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://yoast.com">Yoast</a>. Whoopity Doo!</p>";s:7:"content";s:12:"Array\n			\n		";s:3:"wfw";a:1:{s:10:"commentrss";s:53:"http://yoast.com/wordpress-seo-content-analysis/feed/";}s:5:"slash";a:1:{s:8:"comments";s:2:"67";}s:5:"media";a:2:{s:7:"content";s:4:"\n			";s:13:"content_title";s:16:"content analysis";}s:7:"summary";s:432:"<p>We&#8217;ve been rather busy with the WordPress SEO plugin the last few days. We did a release yesterday and a quick follow up today to fix a few collisions with other plugins. Loads of cool small fixes in there, but one in particular that I think is worth highlighting as it&#8217;s something other plugin developers&#8230;</p><p>T